lead_paragraph: World champions New Zealand were challenged for 50 minutes but still ran in six tries to beat Australia 37-10 in Auckland on Saturday and become the first top tier nation to win 18 consecutive test matches.

headline.print_headline: New Zealand Tame Australia for Record 18th Win
